Bella-Shmurda.-Credit-Artists-Official-Facebook-page.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bella-Shmurda.-Credit-Artists-Official-Facebook-page-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bella-Shmurda.-Credit-Artists-Official-Facebook-page-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bella-Shmurda.-Credit-Artists-Official-Facebook-page-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bella-Shmurda.-Credit-Artists-Official-Facebook-page-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bella-Shmurda.-Credit-Artists-Official-Facebook-page-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>尼日利亚明星贝拉·什穆尔达 (Bella Shmurda) 向已故非洲节奏歌手莫巴德 (MohBad) 致敬，同时批评了莫巴德 (MohBad) 签约的马里安唱片公司 (Marlian Records)。</p><p>这位非洲节奏歌手是尼日利亚的新兴天才之一，《Ponmo》和《Feel Good》等歌曲已成为热门歌曲。 MohBad 与尼日利亚歌手 Naira Marley 创建的唱片公司 Marlain Records 签约，但于 2022 年离开了该唱片公司。</p><p>本月早些时候莫巴德突然去世后，粉丝们将愤怒的矛头指向了马利唱片公司和马莱恩唱片公司，因为这位歌手在离开唱片公司后所经历的“恐惧、痛苦和磨难”。尼日利亚发起了一份拥有超过 126,000 个签名的<a href="https://www.premiumtimesng.com/entertainment/music/625884-over-126000-nigerians-sign-petition-on-mohbad.html#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请愿书</a>，呼吁禁止该品牌。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwwEtYkoc2m/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; 